  "text": "The following figure supplement is available for figure 6: supplement 1D,E) [CITATION_1] . This indicates that these small molecule ER proteostasis regulators phenocopy the capacity of chemical genetic ATF6 activation to selectively reduce secretion of destabilized, amyloidogenic TTR variants relative to the wild-type protein.",
